channel.title: The Geoff Show
channel.description:
The Geoff Show was a humorous radio program, broadcast on Absolute Radio (formerly Virgin Radio) from 3 January 2006 to 25 September 2008. The show ran for three hours, between 10 pm and 1 am, Monday to Thursday. Presented by Geoff Lloyd, it also featured his 'symposium', comprising himself, Annabel Port and his producer Nelson Kumah. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Geoff_Show
